# Docker NGINX PHP(7.4 & 8.1) and SupervisorD using Alpine 3.15
Example PHP-FPM 8.1, PHP-FPM 7.4 & Nginx 1.21 container image for Docker, built on [Alpine Linux](https://www.alpinelinux.org/).

* Built on the lightweight and secure Alpine Linux distribution
* Multi-platform, supporting AMD4, ARMv6, ARMv7, ARM64
* Uses PHP 8.1 for better performance, lower CPU usage & memory footprint
* The services Nginx, nginx config watcher, PHP-FPM and supervisord.
* The logs of all the services are redirected to the output of the Docker container (visible with `docker logs -f <container name>`)

## Description
PHP-FPM, NGINX, NGINX config watcher and Supervisord for Docker build on [Alpine Linux](http://www.alpinelinux.org/).
More information later. 

